<?xml version='1.0' encoding='utf-8'?>

<activity xml:id="act-clasificacionDeTarjetas-rectasNumericas" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"> 

<title>[@@@@@@@@@]</title>

<statement>
  <p>[@@@@@@@@@]</p>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Students may sort by:</p>
<ul>
      <li>The number on the right end of the number line: 1 (B and F) and other than 1 (all others)</li>
      <li>The number of parts from one end of the number line to the other end: 2 (A), 3 (G), 4 (B, D, E), 6 (C, F, H), 8 (I)</li>
      <li>The middle tick mark: labeled (D, H, I) or not labeled (all others)</li>
      <li>What the tick marks represent: whole numbers (A, E, G) or fractions (B, C, D, F, H, I)</li>
    </ul>
  </solution>


